snippet.title: Hitmen Havoc Launch Trailer 2
snippet.description:
Hitmen Havoc is a cartoony, fast-paced 2D arena party shooter for 2-8 players. Imagine a wild mix of Worms and Unreal Tournament.

Get on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2137300/Hitmen_Havoc/

Join Our Discord:
https://discord.gg/VamuDJbDuz
